Description: This is a white telecaster. Standard Mexican with two Humbuckers. Two Humbuckers allow players to get the warm and hot tones needed for soloing and playing harder music without sacrificing the neck feel that Fender players have come to love. There are no obvious defects (paint chips, dents, etc.) I got it without one cover over one of the pickups. $3 part of you want to cover it back up. Plays great!
